snippet.title: Vengeful Heart - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Vengeful Heart launches on August 28th 2020!

Find the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1101310/Vengeful_Heart/
Or find the game on Itch.io: https://salmon-snake.itch.io/vengeful-heart-full-game

Follow our future endeavors: https://twitter.com/VengefulHeart1
Trailer edited by KotoriWorks: https://twitter.com/WorksKotori
Trailer music by Dzod: https://soundcloud.com/dzod
